        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Magic is power, and there are always those who will use power for the art of battle. You may have studied in the military of a nation of the brink of warâ€”Cheliax and Andoran perhaps, or Geb and Nex. You summon whirling energies that can lay waste to both soldiers and armies, while being sure not to neglect arcane countermeasures for common tactical complications or the shields and defenses that keep combatants alive on the battlefield.</p>\n<p><strong>Curriculum</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>cantrips:</strong> shield, telekinetic projectile</li>\n<li><strong>1st:</strong> breathe fire, force barrage, mystic armor</li>\n<li><strong>2nd:</strong> mist, resist energy</li>\n<li><strong>3rd:</strong> earthbind, fireball</li>\n<li><strong>4th:</strong> wall of fire, weapon storm</li>\n<li><strong>5th:</strong> howling blizzard, impaling spike</li>\n<li><strong>6th:</strong> chain lightning, disintegrate</li>\n<li><strong>7th:</strong> energy aegis, true target</li>\n<li><strong>8th:</strong> arctic rift, desiccate</li>\n<li><strong>9th:</strong> falling stars</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>School Spells</strong> initial: force bolt; advanced: energy absorption</p>"
